<body>
<div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_000941_0001" n="0001"/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><add place="inspace" rend="gray diagonal" hand="#U">1/157</add> <space extent="1" unit="words"/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/><placeName>Mission House</placeName>
<lb/><space extent="3" unit="words"/><placeName>Blomfield <choice><abbr>St</abbr><expan>Street</expan></choice></placeName>
<lb/><space extent="3" unit="words"/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/><placeName><settlement type="city">London</settlement></placeName> <date when="1856-01-06">6<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> <choice><abbr>Jan</abbr><expan>January</expan></choice>
<lb/><space extent="6" unit="words"/>1856</date></p>
<lb/>    
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">Dear Sir</p>
<lb/><p><space extent="1" unit="words"/>The time which
<lb/>I can spend in <placeName><country>England</country></placeName>
<lb/>is so very short
<lb/>I am obliged to decline
<lb/>all invitations of
<lb/>the kind you mention
<lb/>and even were it
<lb/>otherwise I am unfitted

	<pb facs="liv_000941_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>for lecturing in
<lb/>English by long
<lb/>disuse of that tongue
<lb/>and a firm conviction
<lb/>that my sphere of
<lb/>usefulness does not
<lb/>lie in public exhibitions
<lb/>at all. I hope then
<lb/>you will kindly
<lb/>make my excuse
<lb/>to the <orgName><choice><orig>young men's</orig><reg>Young Men's</reg></choice>
<lb/><lb/>

	<pb facs="liv_000941_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/><choice><orig><term type="faith">christian</term> association</orig><reg>Christian Association</reg></choice></orgName>
<lb/>some of them may
<lb/>yet be <term type="occupation">missionaries</term>
<lb/>themselves and
<lb/>may be able to
<lb/>supply at some future
<lb/>time my lack of
<lb/>service so the <unclear>Â£ 5</unclear><!-- I'm not sure what to gleam here. Not sure if covered by tape. Could be "D 5", but I don't know what that could refer to. BL--><!-- Fixed. AW -->
<lb/>need not be
<lb/><unclear cert="low">back though</unclear><!-- Could possibly be "book", but I'm not confident in that choice. BL--><!-- legible text, I just can't figure out what word. BL--><!-- Gave it a shot. AW -->
<lb/>cannot come, yet
<lb/>I <choice><sic>dont</sic><corr>don't</corr></choice> say "Give it."

	<pb facs="liv_000941_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>wishing the <orgName><choice><orig>association</orig><reg>Association</reg></choice></orgName>
<lb/>much success &amp;
<lb/>thanking you most
<lb/>heartily for your
<lb/>kind offers of
<lb/>hospitality</p> <closer><salute>I am
<lb/>Dear Sir Most
<lb/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>Sincerely your</salute>
<lb/><space extent="3" unit="chars"/><signed><persName>David Livingstone</persName></signed></closer>



            </div>
